8 Section 1. R.S. 46:2527 is hereby enacted to read as follows:
9 §2527. Women's Health Consortium
10 A. There is hereby established within the Louisiana Department of Health,
11 office on women's health and community health, the Women's Health Consortium.
12 B. The consortium shall be comprised of the following members:
13 (1) One member who is the surgeon general or his designee.
14 (2) One member who is the executive director of the Louisiana State Board
15 of Medical Examiners or his designee.
16 (3) One member from the Pennington Biomedical Research Center
17 specializing in the areas of women's health appointed by the executive director of the
18 Pennington Biomedical Research Center.
19 (4) One member from the Tulane School of Medicine specializing in the
20 areas of women's health appointed by the dean of the Tulane School of Medicine.
